    "body":  "Description: The vision states we must \"match qualifications against job/task requirements in real-time\". We need a logic engine that compares a User\u0027s structured qualifications against a specific Role\u0027s requirements.\n\nAcceptance Criteria:\n\n[ ] Create a RoleRequirement model (e.g., \"Must have GMP Training \u003e 2023\").\n[ ] Create a service function calculateCompliance(userId, roleId).\n[ ] The function returns a status: Qualified, Gap Detected, or Expired.\n[ ] If a gap is found, the system flags the specific missing skill/document.\n\nContext for Copilot:\n\nThis should be a pure function or service that can be called via API.\nComparison logic needs to handle dates (e.g., \"Is the certificate older than 1 year?\").\nReturn a detailed object: { isCompliant: boolean, missingRequirements: [] }.",
